wiki.content:
This track is off Spears' sixth studio album, Circus. The song has not yet been released as a single and no plans to do so have been announced. It has a driving dance feel to the song. It is a declaration of Spears' acceptance of her fame.

track.name: Kill the Lights
comments: Britney needs more Danja... [47] ♥ more more more Danja

This song is so different from Blackout. It definitely fit much better on Circus because pretty much every song sounded different and her vocals are much clearer on the album. Anybody else get Madonna vibes during "there's more to me than what you SEEEEE?"
You are the star now, welcome to the big league! They all wanna pick, they all wanna see, see, see, what you're made of, what you're gonna do... Is life gonna get the best of you?
